# S01-T07: Chat UI & Logic

## Objective
Implement the main Chat screen with message history and typing indicators.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `Chat.vue` view implemented.
- `useChat.js` composable for state management.
- Message bubbles for AI and User.
- Auto-scroll to bottom on new messages.

## Steps
1. Port UI from `bankir-vue-mvp.html`.
2. Implement `useChat` composable.
3. Add markdown rendering for AI responses.
